org.apache.flink.runtime.checkpoint.savepoint

类 FsSavepointStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.checkpoint.savepoint.FsSavepointStore
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    SavepointStore

    public class FsSavepointStore
extends Object
implements SavepointStore
    A file system based SavepointStore.

    Stored savepoints have the following format: 

     MagicNumber SavepointVersion Savepoint
   - MagicNumber => int
   - SavepointVersion => int (returned by Savepoint#getVersion())
   - Savepoint => bytes (serialized via version-specific SavepointSerializer)

                      throws Exception
        从接口复制的说明: SavepointStore
        Disposes the savepoint at the specified path.

        The class loader is needed, because savepoints can currently point to arbitrary snapshot StateHandle instances, which need the user code class loader for deserialization.
